rows.name:
Luxuria's staple food is our very own
homemade porridge. Eat up!

rows.label: tlk44600181_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Why, Owner, you came here especially
to eat some porridge? I'm flattered!

rows.label: tlk44600181_01_msg0006
rows.name:
They're healthy, hearty and it'll warm
you up from the inside out! Believe me,
you'll be hooked!
